{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act19side", "eventName": "綠野幻夢", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DV-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "掙脫美夢", "storyInfo": "眾人發現，操縱神秘生物的其實是受試者集體的意識，這讓實驗的真正目的顯得更為可怖。塞雷婭推測出了斐爾迪南的野心，但幾人多次嘗試，仍未能與白面鴞同步。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.8, "crossfade": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "29_i03", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 30.0, "yTo": 30.0, "duration": 40.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 0.85, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 0.85, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨大的機器在黑暗之中沉默著。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "交錯的纜線就像蔓延的植物根莖，節點點綴著沉甸甸的苞芽。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一個苞芽都是一組發著微光的電極，從下方的生命體中汲取著養分。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失蹤的拓荒者們頭戴電極，一個挨著一個，圍躺在一起。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們仍在正常呼吸，可彷彿對外面發生的一切都無知無覺。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整間實驗室裡最顯眼的，是流淌在所有纜線裡，並彙集在最中央的儀器中的銀色液體。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起神態奇異的幾十名受試者，它才像是真正“活著”。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會這樣......", "name": "埃琳娜"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......海倫？", "name": "埃琳娜"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼......", "name": "埃琳娜"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g5_laboratory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迪克，蓋爾，索菲亞！", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都在這裡......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放了他們。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請小聲些，好不好？我們會嚇到他們的。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，再等一等......等我解決眼前的小問題。一定會沒事的，朋友們，我保證。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你在對他們說話？他們恐怕聽不見。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的生命體徵，我只在昏迷的喬伊絲身上見過。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些電極和銀色液體......說不定正連接著他們的中樞神經系統。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西，為什麼......海倫也在這裡？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她擔心自己無法通過斐爾迪南的考核，於是我為她提供了一個建議。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "建議......是指讓她也變成受試者？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海倫早上還在和我們說笑，現在卻像根木頭似的躺在這裡......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想救她，埃琳娜。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能感受到，她有多麼痛苦......就像我能感受到他們所有人的痛苦一樣。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海倫的貸款幾乎拖垮了他們一整個家庭。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她每天都生活在恐慌中......假如斐爾迪南真的將她開除的話，她甚至會考慮結束自己的生命。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是......我在這裡停下，他們只能回到最悲慘的命運之路上。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼忍心做這麼殘忍的事？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......停下。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停下你這些自以為是的發言，否則的話，我真的不保證自己不會在下一秒就射穿你的腦袋。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼，你對我的憤恨，來自於你對眼前事物和對我的不理解。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我理解你。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒謬！", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你理解我們，所以準備“恩賜”給我們一些新的機會，讓我們除了死在天災下、死在野獸口中之外，再多一條路——", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在大公司的實驗室變成一具具勉強活著的屍體？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多麼慷慨的提議！", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自己難道就沒有想過嗎，桑尼？為什麼......為什麼一樣是得了礦石病，有的人還能繼續工作，有的人卻只能背井離鄉？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用你告訴我。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在醫院給出診斷之後的第二天，我就同時收到了保險合約和解雇通知書。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保險合約有五百六十九頁，解雇通知書卻只有薄薄半張紙。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很少有公司願意雇傭一名感染者，除非這名感染者能證明自己值得公司為他支付這筆巨額保險費——", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道不覺得......這是多麼不公平？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這還用說？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你也該理解我。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g7_mainstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......聯繫不上赫默和格雷伊。", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "基地恐怕完全被封閉了。", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_249_muesys_1#7"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾......迪南。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#7"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "封閉實驗室只會是手段，而不是目的。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來斐爾迪南會在359號基地有大動作。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#8$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，赫默他們會有危險。", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們收不到任何基地內的資訊......是否立刻支援？", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "白面鴞......;......九號裝置。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line120", "option2": "line120"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "九號裝置的資料傳輸的確不同於正常通訊......只要信號有一瞬間的恢復，我們就能看到白面鴞看到的東西。", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我這就試著同步白面鴞。", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......弗蘭克斯女士，您確定您要獨自一個人去見他？"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我拿到了管理局的許可。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說那個叫洛肯·威廉姆斯的人是個瘋子，拿人體做很殘酷的實驗，被判了一百多年。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，我以前聽過他的講座。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些科學家是不是都挺瘋的？咳咳，抱歉，我忘了您也是......像您這樣溫柔端莊的女士，一定跟他們都不一樣。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白，您只是想提醒我注意安全。我會小心的，謝謝。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您預計會在裡面逗留多久？"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個小時。有必要的話，我下周同一時間還會再過來一趟。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有這麼多想跟他聊的？他可不怎麼理會其他人啊......"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許......是因為別人都是想向他索取什麼。而我......我想請求他幫我。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g5_laboratory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.8, "crossfade": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都該獲得平等的機會，天賦的差異不該決定任何人的人生走向。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當任何有天賦的人因為自己的天賦獲得特權的時候，他都在結果上侵佔了其他人的利益，破壞了公平。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就是那個既得利益者，我為自己的“幸運”而羞愧。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡的每一個人......迪克，海倫，還有你，桑尼，我只是想在泥水將你們吞沒之前......拉住你們。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我所做的一切努力，都是希望有一天......幸運只青睞足夠努力的人，而不再偏袒所謂的天賦者。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多年來，我一直在嘗試。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "改造個體，來讓他們變得更強大，並不能解決問題。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天生強大的人，也能透過改造來變得更強，他們甚至還能搶佔先機，在新的賽道上拉出更大的鴻溝。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想要真正的平等，我只能......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你想抹除個體的差距？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#5$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失去意識的受試者......有情緒反應的源石技藝造物......這巨大的將他們連接在一起的儀器......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#5$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你在做的實驗是......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#4$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說過類似的實驗，但我還以為這是早已失敗的狂想......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#4$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......狂想？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有哪一種技術本身是“瘋狂”的，技術只是實現不同理想的手段。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "個體的差距與生俱來，我們不必忽視或者忘記它，但也不必一生受它所累。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "透過我的技術，人們將能更平等地感受彼此，也將更平等地感受土地、空氣與雨水。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "險隘將無法阻擋步伐，風暴也將不再遮蔽視線。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必忍受跋涉之苦，不必與骨肉至親分離，人們就能更安全地眺望遠方。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們難道看不見......這樣的未來有多美好？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我是不是從來都沒有真的搞明白過？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這究竟是個什麼實驗啊......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜，我們一直在找銀色造物背後的施術者。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到剛才，我們都以為是這一個個拓荒者，其實並不是。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "施術者是他們全部。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你有一雙非常敏銳的眼睛，赫默醫生。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗蘭克斯主任，你所描繪的未來只是......你的想像。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我看到的......我看到的是另一番景象。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個源石技藝卓越的術師就能輕鬆摧毀一棟樓，三個卓越的術師能感知並控制一整個街區——", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那把幾十個、上百個乃至上千個人的力量融合起來呢？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大地上的每一個角落都將逃不脫它的“注視”，再堅固的堡壘也不過是它隨手就能捏碎的玩具。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你所關心的這些人，你口中的朋友，他們在想要利用這技術的人眼中，永遠都只是實驗品。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些失敗的......失敗的可能還好一些。那些人對失敗品沒興趣，願意放任他們自生自滅。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成功的“幸運兒”才是最不幸的。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從實驗成功的那一天起，他們就只能活在企業和政府的監控下。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利維亞......我從來沒見過你這樣......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣憤怒。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默感覺到了自己的怒火，她的大腦嗡嗡作響，過往的一幕幕接二連三地浮現出來，將理性與修養撞得七零八落。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確實會改變他們的命運，可代價呢？他們會永遠失去自由，也失去自己的人生！", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我會保護他們。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#3$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我願意付出我的生命......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#3$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許在這裡殺了你，對所有人而言才是最安全的。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這是你們的最終決定......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會反抗。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼，千萬別衝動！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......烏比卡博士，我沒有衝動。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我比任何時候都要清醒。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西·弗蘭克斯......我必須承認，你描繪的未來很有吸引力。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop